rows.label: qst201809_msg0001
rows.name:
Look, Uka. There's a Phonex settlement
even in a place like this.

rows.label: qst201809_msg0002
rows.name:
Even in a place like this, the
Phonexes are living cheerfully...

rows.label: qst201809_msg0003
rows.name: Now, Uka, I'm sure you know, but...

rows.label: qst201809_msg0005
rows.name:
But I wonder if there's anything
they like around here.

rows.label: qst201809_msg0006
rows.name:
It would be good if we could get
some information somewhere...
